{"title":"懒人没有腿（阿拉伯谚语）","authors":["胡安备"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":1,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"懒人没有腿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（阿拉伯谚语）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑伤肉体，话伤灵魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懒人没有腿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驴子去寻找牛角，结果丢了耳朵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时常移植的树很少会长得茂盛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位学者的错误就像是一只失事的船，它将会使很多的人遭难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡安备  辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}